 37. Explain Kafka partitioning strategy.
 ==============================================================================
  Three strategies:
				a) Round Robin
					Msg1 → P0
					Msg2 → P1
					Msg3 → P2
				
				b) Key-Based Partitioning
					Account123 → P1
					Account123 → P1
					Account123 → P1
				
				c) Custom Partitioner
					VIP Customers → P0
					Normal Customers → P1



  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  